Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.98,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,The dream I had when I was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:48.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子供の頃の夢は 色褪せない落書きで
