Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.31,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,were drawn to my heart's desire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.98,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k27}o{\k29}mo{\k36}u {\k28}ma{\k42}ma {\k16}ka{\k23}ki {\k31}su{\k31}be{\k60}rase{\k30}te
